OL,3,CPoliticians propose ban on selling
OL,4,Cvapes to children in Guernsey
OL,6,FThe sale of vapes to under-18s could
OL,7,Fbe banned in under plans to toughen
OL,8,Frules around smoking and e-cigarettes.
OL,10,FUnlike the UK, there are currently no
OL,11,Frestrictions over who can buy them on
OL,12,Fthe island - leaving the decision down
OL,13,Fto the individual sellers.
OL,15,FGuernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,16,FCommittee want this to change,
OL,17,Fproposing that vapes can only be
OL,18,Fbought by adults and disposable vapes
OL,19,Fshould be banned altogether.
