OL,6,FThey also want to make it an offence
OL,7,Fto smoke in vehicles carrying children
OL,8,Fdue to the health concerns of second-
OL,9,Fhand inhalation.
OL,11,FIt comes after reports children as in
OL,12,Fthe Channel Islands.
OL,14,FIn , the number of secondary school
OL,15,Fpupils who vape regularly has risen
OL,16,Ffrom 2% in 2019 to 10% in 2022.
