OL,6,FDeputy Al Brouard, Committee
OL,7,FPresident, says: "The Committee shares
OL,8,Fthe concerns held in the community
OL,9,Fabout young people using vapes and has
OL,10,Ftaken a pragmatic approach to
OL,11,Frecommend regulatory measures to
OL,12,Freduce their visibility and
OL,13,Favailability."
