OL,6,FDr Nicola Brink, Director of Public
OL,7,FHealth, says she recognises that vapes
OL,8,Fare "useful in helping some adults
OL,9,Fgive up smoking" but believes "it is
OL,10,Fconcerning to see that the packaging
OL,11,Fand flavouring of many of these
OL,12,Fproducts appear to be targeting
OL,13,Fchildren".
